::Shadow Wing::

She pulled the dagger out of her leg. She groaned at the pain.  She 
looked over at Torca and Prowl, "How are you guys holding up?"  She 
yelled at Lunarpine, "So glad you could join the party."
She wiped the fluid of the blade of the dagger threw it at Ares.  She 
drew her gun again and shot at Sixshot.
